{"tid":1745043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界同我十點前投票！！！","createTime":"2019-11-22T04:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T04:59:24.000Z","uid":49595,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"406fffab9e48e52ac77528b4447acf1414955227","tid":1745043,"uid":49595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"轉寄：<br />\n只要票站開左3個鐘都會計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n馮驊說，只要有票站持續三小時有混亂，即停止選舉。即只要早上十點後關票站，都會計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n怪不得有建制派攪飲早茶團，今次調轉來，係朝早7點投完票先一齊去飲茶。<br />\n<br />\n呢招果然絕呀！<br />\n<br />\n同埋只要建制早上一夠票，即刻派人扮黑衣人在選舉站前搗亂，然後大有藉口把選舉煞停，咁就 sure win.....<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔理真定假，大家早起身一日！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c00768b44959868684263fcc0d24b114307c4e53","tid":1745043,"uid":49595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"1124 十點前投票！"},{"pid":"fb1d781cdd41fb236b19a42d54fdbac161ec84f3","tid":1745043,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"推 最好7點投"},{"pid":"e351032f77b1e4c3efe6e3f4bd72fed4198515b3","tid":1745043,"uid":244183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"屌你！未開站好坐定喺出面等開站"},{"pid":"decf38f615a99ca9f0875d4e9035a95b9ccf7462","tid":1745043,"uid":235716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:41:35.000Z","msg":"大家早起黎明投票啦"},{"pid":"23fb6b01cf0f9b9e3eb0eeabcbdbf26ce24b791d","tid":1745043,"uid":49595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e351032f77b1e4c3efe6e3f4bd72fed4198515b3","tid":1745043,"uid":244183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"屌你！未開站好坐定喺出面等開站"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"對唔住大佬 你岩 7點落樓！"}]}